हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: Jhanvi is getting married when she gets to know that her best friend and her husband were cheating on her. In the marriage venue when her marriage broke off, there is a stir in the audience who will take her as a wife now. Then one gentlemen from the crowd comes forward. But who is this gentlemen, Is he a normal person ?
